column4: NSLOCTEXT("[7770CFE549D49C41378594BA558346D2]", "44E7B2DA4523007BFBA8738FB3323B9C", "It\'s amazing that you made it through the forest!")
NSLOCTEXT("[7770CFE549D49C41378594BA558346D2]", "7FE9A5B14BE251E414D9B7A06A99F52E", "I am Centarumon. I\'m sorry for what I did.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7770CFE549D49C41378594BA558346D2]", "5071C1494E6E81FFF0868396EE2D1784", "I didn\'t test you for fun. I want to work with you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7770CFE549D49C41378594BA558346D2]", "7D34355247E243AF3DFFB68025B5E313", "Go on. I\'ll stay in the city and wait for you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[7770CFE549D49C41378594BA558346D2]", "D9133DD144F9CE9E6D8DA0BD43290065", "{Partner}, I think we\'re getting pretty famous.")
